data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This charming residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a spacious 1669 sq ft, offering ample space for comfortable living. The property features a backyard, perfect for entertaining guests. The Sellers are very motived and are relocating out of state. The Sellers are eager to make a deal, presenting a fantastic opportunity for potential buyers. With play areas and parks close by for kids, there are also great friendly neighbors. This home is nestled in a welcoming community. The house is ready for you to personalize and make it your own. Don't miss out on this wonderful chance to call this place home!
